&lt;li&gt;Substring Search: Knuth-Morris-Pratt, Boyer-Moore, Rabin-Karp.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pattern Matching: Regular expressions (regex).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data Compression: Huffman &amp;amp; LZW compression. (trie plays an
important role!)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
